title: Clinton seeks to move past email woes in Democratic debate
text: > Top News Clinton seeks to move past email woes in Democratic debate People chant during a rally in front of the Trump Hotel Monday, Oct. 12, 2015, in Las Vegas. Democratic presidential candidate Hillary Rodham Clinton spoke at the rally held by the Culinary Union to support a union drive at the Trump Hotel in Las Vegas. The hotel tower in back right belongs to the Wynn, where a Democratic presidential debate will be held Tuesday.(AP Photo/John Locher)
